- Instantly move your data with the auto-delete function.
- Supports videos, GIFs, Live Photos, Slo-mo, and Time-lapse, with a built-in video player.
- You can restore photos and videos back to the iPhone Photos app.
- Set any photo as your album cover.
- Saves photos in high resolution to keep your memories sharp.
- Add notes and comments to your important moments with the memo feature.
- Enjoy looking back on your memories with the built-in slideshow.
- Share photos and videos through AirDrop, social media, email, messages, and other supported apps.
- With Dropbox support, you can transfer your data wirelessly.
